{"tid":1758941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人唔係攰唔係抖，係用咗一票，寄望議員用更大力去反抗！","createTime":"2019-11-27T11:01:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T00:52:48.000Z","uid":74778,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5241894452fe35fba95d534d2c6e38a2657b4660","tid":1758941,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:01:21.000Z","msg":"<strong>你地所得嘅每一票都有血有淚，係香港人用條命換返黎!<br />\n<br />\n今次嘅全民覺醒，係勝利，亦都係新挑戰嘅開始！<br />\n喺無大台之下，民主派全面入主區議會，下一步立法會，直接威脅中央喺香港大小議會嘅影響力。中央一定無所不用其極咁修例、DQ、搬龍門、分化... 再同中央玩贏賬面數，佢一搬龍門真係可以乜都無<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地真係要無比咁團結，去建構黃色經濟圈，真正和勇不分。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">由區議員帶頭，成立基金！資援前線手足！香港係佢地打返黎嫁！</span><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，缺一不可!<br />\n團結香港，和勇不分!</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求係首要! 但最終目標係真正和勇不分，同建制完全割蓆，唔再對對面有任何依賴! <strong>真正黃色經濟圈!</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求:</span></span></strong><br />\n即刻要林鄭下台無可能，亦都無必要。佢做到成pat屎咁，中共想佢落台之前做多幾次醜人，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地都一樣逼到佢咁做！我地要逼到佢做我地嘅醜人！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一樣！<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">一定係清算黑警！</span></strong>獨立調查委員會，由大法官吹雞，調查6月9日至今<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>所有</strong></span>黑警執勤、當值、調查、扣留巿民、同黑社會組織關係等，<br />\n是否合法、<br />\n有否濫捕、<br />\n有否濫用私刑、<br />\n有否非謀殺、<br />\n有否非法處理屍體(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咸左)<br />\n是否違反人道守則！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n特赦所有手足！<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">6月9至今所有被捕人士都要得到公平審理！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正式撤回逃犯引導條例，雖然已經做左，但<strong>立法係建基於大多數民眾利益</strong>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">政府必須承諾以後<strong>行政立法司法</strong>，都必須以香港人權利為首要考慮及出發點!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而社會因為政府6月9日至10月23日(共137日)堅持唔肯撤回逃犯引導條例而出現嚴重撕裂，大量人命傷亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">特區政府必須負上全部責任!</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n制定真普選時間表!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和勇不分，建構黃色經濟圈</span></span></strong><br />\n今次民主派，泛民所得嘅每一票，都係全香港，不分和勇，用條命去激起全民覺醒咁換返黎!<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">由區議員帶頭，成立基金！資援前線手足！</span>可以安撫人心，而且宜家香港人為社運搞眾籌唔係難事，仲要係幫助一D為香港流血嘅手足!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最終目標係真正和勇不分，同建制完全割蓆，唔再對對面有任何依賴! <strong>建構真正黃色經濟圈!</strong><br />\n<br />\n例如:<br />\nTecky Academy決定將全額資助因社運而被捕的人士報讀「人工智能及程式設計微學位」，希望有助各位於日後留港／外地發展。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tecky.io/photos/a.1242620759210318/1553069384832119?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftecky.io%2Fphotos%2Fa.1242620759210318%2F1553069384832119%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mROaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=76b1dae2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tecky.io/photos/a.1242620759210318/1553069384832119?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n利，從未聽過呢間野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">做住先！唔該！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">之後嘅路只能寄望民主派當選議員唔好再分化分裂，真係做返d巿民想做嘅野!!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e69ef80d286c0820705f3fac1cbb1ece908c7b3b","tid":1758941,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06893733a8f4f0c46cc5bdef2d325b83de120d0f","tid":1758941,"uid":198773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e2a04ee68d238a907792126537838ed6ef16eb","tid":1758941,"uid":223616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6R0kn46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6R0kn46.png&h=8a6ce961&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17d08f27441152b63b199b7d802af0387d84f245","tid":1758941,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10e2a04ee68d238a907792126537838ed6ef16eb","tid":1758941,"uid":223616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6R0kn46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna